title: Ubehage's Window Troll
description:
Ubehage's Window Troll
----------------------

This is a small and annoying application.

It will create a random window somewhere on the screen.
Just a normal, blank window.
When the user closes this window, 2 more windows will pop up.

And so on.....

If the user tries to shut down Windows, the shutdown will be cancelled and a message will pop up telling the user that they're being trolled.


/Ubehage
